headline: 3Q Profit Margins for Aggregate Blues Plans Analyzed by Mark Farrah Associates
summary: PITTSBURGH, February 05, 2026--MFA assessed profit margin trends of Blue Cross Blue Shield (BCBS) plans, and compared year-over-year performance, as of September 2025.
